title: Cant join clubs
body: Ok so i just transfered from NA to EU west and now im not able to join any clubs. can someone please help me know why??

replies.body: Maybe you're underage, do they serve alcohol at these clubs?

Hmm.. we'll need to take a closer look at what happened in order to resolve this together. I recommend reaching out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can do so.
